have the opportunity to visit China and to exchange views with
leaders of the CPC and the Chinese government, and that he hopes
the visit and exchange of ideas will increase mutual understanding
and bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
The LDP delegation arrived here Monday as guests of the
International Department of the CPC Central Committee. 
