<HEADLINE> Chinese Rugby Association Recognized as IRFB Member </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, March 18 (Xinhua) -- The Chinese Rugby Football
Association (CRFA) was officially recognized as a member of The
International Rugby Football Board (IRFB) here on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
