thus become the 76th and newest member of the rugby's world
governing body.
</P>
<P>
And, as a consequence of the admission by IRFB of the
Beijing-based CRFA, the rugby union located in Taipei will retain
its membership under the new name of Chinese Taipei RFU, the IRFB
announced.  
