<HEADLINE> Shanghai Stock Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 18 (Xinhua) -- The SSE-30 index, based on 30
blue chips that are selected from more than 200 A shares for
domestic investors on the Shanghai Stock Exchange, closed at
3,235.23, up 20.17 points from the previous session, according to
the China Finance Trust and Investment Corporation.
</P>
<P>
