<HEADLINE> Drugs Seized in East China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANCHANG, March 18 (Xinhua) -- The police in east China's
Jiangxi province reportedly confiscated 98.5 g of heroin.
</P>
<P>
