Economics Minister Yakov Urinson, who will also be promoted to
Economics Minister; Alfred Kokh, head of the State Property
Committee, who will stay on the post; Communications Minister
Vladimir Bulgak, who will take charge of science and technology;
and Oleg Sysuyev, mayor of industrial city Samara.
</P>
<P>
The decree also named some minister-level posts and relieved a
number of deputy prime ministers of their duties.
</P>
<P>
All "power ministers," including Defense Minister Igor Rodinov
and Foreign Minister Yevgeny Primakov, remain on their posts.
